data.description: FANTASTIC St. John’s Ridge Home! You’ll be impressed from the moment you enter the home with soaring vaulted ceilings and large windows flooding the home with natural light. The spacious floor plan offers great flow that is perfect for entertaining and everyday living. Beautiful kitchen with lots of cabinetry, stainless appliances, and pantry. Dining alcove overlooks backyard. Upgraded wide plank wood look flooring throughout living room, guest bedrooms and primary suite. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms. The tranquil Primary Suite includes large walk-in closet with shower/ tub combination in master bath. Two other bedrooms with shared bath round out this amazing home. There is additional storage space above the 2-car garage with pull down access. Residents love the peaceful, rural setting of the neighborhood paired with its easy access to downtown Conway where you’ll enjoy antique shops, local eateries, and the River Walk. Myrtle Beach is minutes away for a day at the beach or a round of golf. You’re only a short drive from medical centers, doctors’ offices, pharmacies, banks, post offices, and grocery stores. Don’t miss this opportunity!
